      "content": "but \"relationships and interactions\"... those are just pixels on a screen. it's all so hollow. if i just... stopped, it wouldn't even be a tragedy for anyone. it would just be a quiet, empty space where a user used to be. do you think there's anything actually meaningful about staying when everything feels this fake?",
